    • Enum Constant Detail

      • READ_ONLY

        public static final IDfFilterOrderDependency.Dependency READ_ONLY
        These filters are called first. A typical READ_ONLY filter is used to log user activity, without modifying the search behaviour

  • TARGET_LANGUAGE_INDEPENDENT

    public static final IDfFilterOrderDependency.Dependency TARGET_LANGUAGE_INDEPENDENT
    A typical filter is independent of the target language and will not force the target language either.

  • MODIFY_TARGET_LANGUAGE

    public static final IDfFilterOrderDependency.Dependency MODIFY_TARGET_LANGUAGE
    Indicate a filter that potentially changes the target language of the generated query. For example, a filter that call IDfQueryBuilder.setDatabaseSearchRequested(boolean) and that depends on the query itself to make this decision.

  • TARGET_LANGUAGE_DEPENDENT

    public static final IDfFilterOrderDependency.Dependency TARGET_LANGUAGE_DEPENDENT
